Pronotum (
Fig. 13
) narrower than elytra, convex, slightly longer than wide, widest at middle. Sides almost parallel, slightly narrowed from anterior third. Posterior angles with distinct short carina. Lateral carina distinct, complete anteriorly.

Pregenital segments and aedeagus as in 
Figs 22–26
. Tergite VIII (
